https://laravel-news.com/package-auto-discovery

https://github.com/barryvdh/laravel-debugbar/pull/643/files

将下面的添加到 composer.json 中

"extra": {
    "laravel": {
        "providers": [
            "Foo\\Bar\\ServiceProvider"
        ],
        "aliases": {
            "Bar": "Foo\\Bar\\Facade"
        }
    }
}
